## Automation Benefits

* Saves approximately **8 operational hours per month** through automated workflow execution
* Eliminates recurring operational effort for scheduled capacity reporting
* Provides **100% cluster visibility** through centralized reporting
* Enables proactive identification of capacity and garbage collection risks
* Improves reporting consistency and operational accuracy
* Delivers **2 automated reporting cycles daily** without operational dependency
* Strengthens capacity planning through continuous visibility into cluster utilization
* Standardizes cluster-wide reporting across the backup platform
